<h2>Reset Password</h2>
<p class="email-salutation">Hey there,</p>
<p>You recently requested to reset your password for your Phoenix Admin account. Click the button below to reset it.</p>
<p><a href="<%= raw @reset_url %>" class="email-button">Reset your password</a></p>
<p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or reply to let us know. This password reset is only valid for the next 15 minutes.
<p>Thanks,<br>The Phoenix Admin Team</p>
<p class="email-fineprint">If you're having trouble clicking the password reset button, copy and paste the link below into your web browser.</p>
<p><%= raw @reset_url %></p>
